data.text:
Katrina Kaif’s Airport Appearance Sparks New Pregnancy Rumours

Katrina Kaif was recently spotted at Mumbai airport, leaving the city after a prolonged absence from the public eye. A video of her airport appearance has been widely shared on social media, showing her exiting a car that appeared to be driven by her husband, Vicky Kaushal. In the clip, Katrina wore an oversized black tracksuit and carried a matching jacket. This sighting has once again sparked pregnancy speculation among internet users. Previously, Vicky Kaushal had addressed these pregnancy rumors during an event. Katrina Kaif was last seen in Sriram Raghavan's film Merry Christmas.

11 views | 1 hour ago

Actress Ayesha Takia Strikes Back on Instagram with a Subtle Dig at Trolls | Check Out Her Latest Post

In her latest Instagram post, Ayesha Takia has clapped back at online trolls with a subtle yet powerful message. The former Bollywood actress, known for her graceful demeanor, has once again proven that she's not one to shy away from speaking her mind. Fans are buzzing over her recent post, where she skillfully addresses her critics with a touch of class and confidence. Curious to see how she reacted? Watch the complete video now!

668 views | 3 days ago

Ayesha Takia Quits Instagram After Severe Criticism of Her Latest Look

Ayesha Takia recently garnered significant attention when her latest social media post went viral. The actress, known for her role in Wanted, faced intense trolling online over her appearance, which led her to delete her Instagram account in response to the backlash. The controversy erupted after Takia posted a video wearing a kanjeevaram saree and heavy gold jewelry, which sparked a flood of negative comments. Previously, Takia had publicly defended herself against critics of her looks. Notably, Ayesha Takia has not appeared in films since her last role in the 2011 movie Mod.

1633 views | 4 days ago

Thalapathy Vijay Reveals TVK Flag; Critics Draw Parallels with Spain’s Flag

On August 22, Tamil superstar Vijay unveiled the flag and symbol for his political party, Tamizhaga Vetri Kazhagam. Having announced the party’s launch in February, Vijay hoisted the flag at the Panaiyur party office, expressing confidence that "Tamil Nadu will be better from now on. Victory is sure." The flag features maroon and yellow colors with elephants on the sides and a peacock encircled by stars in the center. Videos from the event quickly went viral online. While fans praised Vijay, some noted similarities between the TVK flag and Spain’s flag. Vijay is set to contest in the 2026 Tamil Nadu assembly elections.
